snippet.title: Drum Roll Trailer
snippet.description:
This game is coming soon on Steam.

This is a game where you roll a drum can that is about to explode to the goal.
If you have ever wanted to roll a drum, this is for you!

Steam store page is here↓
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2414600/

Music：BGMer
http://bgmer.net
